1
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:37,080
Officer.

2
00:01:37,479 --> 00:01:38,940
In the French Concession,

3
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:41,400
the property of our Japanese expats

4
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:44,500
is also protected by the French Municipal Council.

5
00:01:44,960 --> 00:01:45,759
Right?

6
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:48,240
The police station treats all residents equally.

7
00:01:48,240 --> 00:01:49,770
We recognize the land deed.

8
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:51,039
I'm sorry, everyone.

9
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:51,920
Mrs. Zhang,

10
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:54,560
control your servants.

11
00:01:54,960 --> 00:01:56,600
The procedures are legal.

12
00:01:56,720 --> 00:01:59,360
It's no use pestering us like this.

13
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:01,320
Be smart.

14
00:02:01,640 --> 00:02:04,120
It's simple and decent.

15
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:05,160
Also,

16
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:06,800
the old man in your family,

17
00:02:06,800 --> 00:02:08,880
I don't know whose strings he pulled,

18
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:10,440
but he was actually released.

19
00:02:10,440 --> 00:02:11,320
But rest assured.

20
00:02:11,320 --> 00:02:13,320
Mr. Fujita is generous.

21
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:14,560
He won't pursue this.

22
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:16,000
He even allows you to go in

23
00:02:16,160 --> 00:02:18,760
and take whatever you want.

24
00:02:18,880 --> 00:02:20,079
What a good man.

25
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:22,280
If you keep making a scene,

26
00:02:22,600 --> 00:02:24,400
Mr. Fujita can always

27
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:27,440
throw you into the Gendarmerie in Hongkou.

28
00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:28,680
By then,

29
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:30,120
the old and the young of your family

30
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:32,000
will be completely helpless

31
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,720
and have nowhere to turn.

32
00:02:34,760 --> 00:02:35,400
Go in.

33
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:36,680
Go.

34
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:38,600
Who dares to move?

35
00:02:38,920 --> 00:02:39,920
You are not allowed to go in.

36
00:02:39,920 --> 00:02:40,480
Who dares to move? What are you doing?

37
00:02:40,480 --> 00:02:40,960
This is our house.

38
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:41,560
What are you doing?

39
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:42,320
This is our house.

40
00:02:42,320 --> 00:02:42,880
What is going on?

41
00:02:42,880 --> 00:02:43,740
No one can go in.

42
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:44,280
Move.

43
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:44,720
Go.

44
00:02:44,720 --> 00:02:45,280
Move.

45
00:02:45,320 --> 00:02:45,680
Go.

46
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:46,600
This is our house.

47
00:02:46,600 --> 00:02:47,480
Are you just going to bully

48
00:02:47,480 --> 00:02:49,600
women, children, and old people?

49
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:51,960
You're leaving us no way to survive.

50
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:53,930
If Zhang Yunqi were here today,

51
00:02:54,200 --> 00:02:55,800
I would tear him apart alive.

52
00:02:56,040 --> 00:02:57,400
Although my surname isn't Zhang,

53
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:58,520
I'm telling you,

54
00:02:58,800 --> 00:03:00,600
I am a member of the Zhangs today.

55
00:03:02,480 --> 00:03:03,240
Madam.

56
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:04,920
I said it before.

57
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:08,480
In my life, I can kneel

58
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:10,280
and bow to others.

59
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,080
Give me a crack,

60
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:14,040
and I can hold up the sky.

61
00:03:14,440 --> 00:03:16,170
But I don't want to kneel today.

62
00:03:16,760 --> 00:03:18,420
And I don't want to bow either.

63
00:03:18,880 --> 00:03:21,600
I've sealed that crack too.

64
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:24,720
I don't care if you are from the police station or the Gendarmerie.

65
00:03:24,720 --> 00:03:27,160
I don't care if you are Japanese or French.

66
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:29,320
If any of you dares to enter this house,

67
00:03:29,320 --> 00:03:31,800
you'll have to step over my dead body.

68
00:03:32,040 --> 00:03:33,280
You want to act like a thug, huh?

69
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:33,810
Let me see

70
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:35,920
who can act more like a thug than us from the police station.

71
00:03:35,920 --> 00:03:36,520
Take them away.

72
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:36,800
Go.

73
00:03:36,880 --> 00:03:37,520
You can't go in.

74
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:37,880
Go.

75
00:03:37,920 --> 00:03:39,200
You are not allowed to go in.

76
00:03:39,200 --> 00:03:40,280
You are not allowed to go in.

77
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:40,960
You are not allowed to go in.

78
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:41,600
Go.

79
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:48,680
I am the owner of this house.

80
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,760
May I say a few words?

81
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:58,560
Mr. Fujita,

82
00:04:00,160 --> 00:04:02,560
this is our second time meeting each other.

83
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:04,800
The first time was in prison.

84
00:04:05,720 --> 00:04:07,200
You used the excuse of him being an anti-Japanese element

85
00:04:07,200 --> 00:04:08,960
to throw my father into prison,

86
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:11,010
and forced him to apologize to you.

87
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:13,240
We wrote the letter.

88
00:04:13,920 --> 00:04:16,120
We apologized.

89
00:04:16,760 --> 00:04:18,519
Today, I got my father out,

90
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,519
and we want to go home.

91
00:04:20,839 --> 00:04:22,040
But you're telling me

92
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:24,440
that our home has become yours.

93
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,640
I don't understand why.

94
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:29,220
Since you Japanese came to China,

95
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:32,240
you've occupied the Three Northeastern Provinces,

96
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,440
you've occupied Nanjing,

97
00:04:33,440 --> 00:04:35,170
and you've occupied Shanghai.

98
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:38,280
We fled all the way from Nanjing to Shanghai.

99
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:40,960
Now, even our last place of refuge,

100
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:43,159
you tell me is your home too.

101
00:04:44,520 --> 00:04:46,600
But do you know what day today is?

102
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:51,240
Today is the day of the Victory at Taierzhuang.

103
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:54,520
I believe on your way here,

104
00:04:54,640 --> 00:04:56,720
you must have heard the firecrackers

105
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:59,760
and the laughter of the Chinese people.

106
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:03,680
I didn't know where Tai'erzhuang was,

107
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:06,280
but this battle showed me

108
00:05:06,280 --> 00:05:08,720
where it is.

109
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,720
Just like last year,

110
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:13,250
I didn't know where Pingxingguan was either.

111
00:05:13,880 --> 00:05:15,400
But that great victory

112
00:05:15,400 --> 00:05:18,280
made all of us Chinese know

113
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:20,800
where Pingxingguan is.

114
00:05:22,280 --> 00:05:23,480
It is these victories

115
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:25,760
that showed us we can win,

116
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:28,400
that we can drive you out of China.

117
00:05:30,960 --> 00:05:33,040
It's true for our country,

118
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:36,080
and it's true for our home.

119
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:39,640
Today, I, Ding Yujiao, stand here,

120
00:05:39,640 --> 00:05:41,440
and I won't take half a step back.

121
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:44,280
If you want to enter my home,

122
00:05:44,760 --> 00:05:47,159
you'll have to step over my dead body.

123
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:53,200
Mrs. Zhang.

124
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:56,040
I am a cultural merchant.

125
00:05:56,840 --> 00:05:58,880
The military matters you mentioned,

126
00:05:58,880 --> 00:06:00,080
I have no interest in.

127
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:04,200
I bought this house for a high price.

128
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:06,600
Take them all away.

129
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:08,720
Mr. Fujita said

130
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:11,080
he bought this house with his own money,

131
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:12,240
and he wants to go home.

132
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:13,040
Officer,

133
00:06:13,320 --> 00:06:14,920
please fulfill your duties.

134
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:15,860
Take them away.

135
00:06:16,640 --> 00:06:17,160
Go.

136
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:18,000
You can't go in.

137
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:18,440
Go.

138
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:19,360
You can't go in.

139
00:06:19,640 --> 00:06:20,680
Wait.

140
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,080
Father.

141
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:28,880
Father, go back.

142
00:06:29,400 --> 00:06:30,360
Wanfu.

143
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:31,140
Master.

144
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,080
Father, go back.

145
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:33,040
Everything is fine here, Father.

146
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:33,500
Go back.

147
00:06:33,640 --> 00:06:34,640
Go back, Master.

148
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:35,080
Father.

149
00:06:35,080 --> 00:06:36,840
My mind is perfectly clear.

150
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:41,240
Hold on.

151
00:06:41,440 --> 00:06:42,600
Hold on.

152
00:06:45,159 --> 00:06:46,520
It really is you.

153
00:06:47,520 --> 00:06:49,280
Wearing Japanese clothes.

154
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:51,650
What a small world for enemies.

155
00:06:52,400 --> 00:06:53,640
Everything you said,

156
00:06:54,280 --> 00:06:55,560
I understood it all.

157
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:58,040
Don't worry.

158
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:02,760
Let me see this contract.

159
00:07:06,440 --> 00:07:07,600
Mr. Fujita.

160
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:10,080
Let him see.

161
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:13,810
This is the land deed and the contract.

162
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:16,060
Master.

163
00:07:16,080 --> 00:07:17,200
Father, no.

164
00:07:17,840 --> 00:07:19,370
I won't resort to violence.

165
00:07:29,200 --> 00:07:30,360
Zhang Yunqi.

166
00:07:31,640 --> 00:07:32,960
It was Zhang Yunqi.

167
00:07:34,880 --> 00:07:36,360
My son is gone.

168
00:07:37,159 --> 00:07:39,480
Zhang Yunqi is my son.

169
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:42,760
The matters between Zhang Yunqi and us,

170
00:07:42,840 --> 00:07:43,600
the grudges,

171
00:07:43,880 --> 00:07:45,680
we will resolve them ourselves.

172
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:49,760
I am the owner of this house,

173
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:52,380
and the head of the family.

174
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,800
Since Zhang Yunqi signed it,

175
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:57,300
and he is a member of the Zhang Family,

176
00:07:58,520 --> 00:07:59,880
this contract,

177
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:02,400
we accept it.

178
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,560
We can't accept this.

179
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:06,000
We cannot.

180
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:07,760
Exactly.

181
00:08:07,880 --> 00:08:09,120
How can we give it to the Japanese?

182
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:10,920
Yujiao, let's move out.

183
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:11,800
Father.

184
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:12,840
Master.

185
00:08:12,960 --> 00:08:13,360
Move.

186
00:08:13,520 --> 00:08:14,840
That's not how it is.

187
00:08:14,960 --> 00:08:16,480
That is exactly how it is.

188
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:24,240
This head must not bow.

189
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:27,640
This back must not bend.

190
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:32,120
Why do we not bend?

191
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:35,000
Because what we Chinese respect is

192
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:39,330
'For life or for death', and 'A promise is worth a thousand pieces of gold'.

193
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:43,120
Chinese people do not bend, but we are reasonable.

194
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:50,720
Yujiao.

195
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:52,120
Move.

196
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:53,560
Master.

197
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:54,680
Move.

198
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:55,480
Go.

199
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:56,730
You can't enter. Go.

200
00:08:56,800 --> 00:08:57,720
You can't enter.

201
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:58,180
Yujiao.

202
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,170
No one can enter.

203
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:01,050
No one can enter!

204
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:04,560
No, this is our house.

205
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:05,980
You are not allowed in.

206
00:09:10,160 --> 00:09:11,040
Yujiao.

207
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,200
Get out of the way.

208
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:13,720
Yujiao.

209
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:17,720
Don't scare the child.

210
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,160
Go.

211
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,520
Sir,

212
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:41,680
you have left a deep impression on me.

213
00:09:42,800 --> 00:09:44,120
I know you now.

214
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,400
Mrs. Zhang.

215
00:09:52,880 --> 00:09:54,120
As far as I know,

216
00:09:54,920 --> 00:09:58,480
one Tai'erzhuang doesn't mean much.

217
00:10:13,520 --> 00:10:14,560
Yujiao.

218
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:16,520
What name did I give

219
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:19,080
to the child?

220
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:23,640
Yueming.

221
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:30,600
Every cloud has a silver lining.

222
00:10:37,160 --> 00:10:38,820
I'll go in and move our things.

223
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:00,800
Wanfu.

224
00:11:01,560 --> 00:11:02,020
Master.

225
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:03,140
You should go back.

226
00:11:03,400 --> 00:11:04,560
It's getting late.

227
00:11:05,760 --> 00:11:07,280
Where would I go back to, Master?

228
00:11:07,280 --> 00:11:08,610
Back to the restaurant.

229
00:11:09,280 --> 00:11:10,720
The restaurant is short-handed.

230
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:12,720
Don't make it difficult for your boss.

231
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:14,250
If I go back, what about you?

232
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:15,920
Us?

233
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:18,860
Don't worry about us anymore.

234
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:21,780
You have taken good enough care of us.

235
00:11:22,520 --> 00:11:24,520
We don't want to burden you anymore.

236
00:11:24,920 --> 00:11:27,440
You are a kind and righteous child.

237
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:29,840
Whatever you do in the future,

238
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:32,080
just do what you want.

239
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:34,300
As long as you are down-to-earth.

240
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:37,380
Please don't, Master.

241
00:11:37,880 --> 00:11:38,680
I,

242
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:41,210
I will go find Boss Xu right now.

243
00:11:42,040 --> 00:11:43,320
Although he is stingy,

244
00:11:43,640 --> 00:11:45,480
he has a sharp tongue but a soft heart.

245
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:46,480
Maybe if I beg him,

246
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:48,530
he will let you all stay.

247
00:11:48,560 --> 00:11:49,320
Wanfu,

248
00:11:50,480 --> 00:11:51,480
don't go.

249
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:54,720
It's not like I haven't been to Lutai Restaurant before.

250
00:11:54,720 --> 00:11:56,000
It's only so big.

251
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:59,160
Your boss is also running an honest business.

252
00:11:59,160 --> 00:12:01,360
It's hard to do business in these times.

253
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:03,960
Adding three more mouths to feed...

254
00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:05,290
If you force us upon him,

255
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:07,440
he might not even keep you.

256
00:12:07,920 --> 00:12:08,680
Yes.

257
00:12:08,920 --> 00:12:10,240
Then what will you do?

258
00:12:13,520 --> 00:12:15,960
I can go find my old classmates,

259
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:17,010
and old friends,

260
00:12:17,480 --> 00:12:18,800
to ask for help.

261
00:12:19,040 --> 00:12:21,700
Don't mention your old classmates and friends.

262
00:12:21,760 --> 00:12:22,800
When you were in your most difficult time,

263
00:12:22,800 --> 00:12:24,080
did they help you?

264
00:12:24,880 --> 00:12:26,540
Let alone where you will live,

265
00:12:26,800 --> 00:12:28,000
do you even know what you will eat for the next meal?

266
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:28,880
Do you?

267
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:38,200
Madam, take this.

268
00:12:38,560 --> 00:12:39,680
This is all I have.

269
00:12:41,480 --> 00:12:42,640
Thank you, Wanfu.

270
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:45,400
But this purse Xiaoyue embroidered for you,

271
00:12:45,400 --> 00:12:46,800
has it ever been full?

272
00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:48,570
Take the money back.

273
00:12:48,600 --> 00:12:49,660
Don't give it to us.

274
00:12:49,800 --> 00:12:51,640
Aren't you going to save it to find Xiaoyue?

275
00:12:51,640 --> 00:12:53,120
Where can I find her?

276
00:12:53,640 --> 00:12:55,970
The Yu family in Wuhan hasn't replied yet.

277
00:12:57,120 --> 00:12:58,000
I guess,

278
00:12:58,440 --> 00:12:59,520
in my life,

279
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:02,130
I probably won't be able to see her.

280
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:04,240
The Luo family hasn't replied either.

281
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:06,400
Maybe they are not in Wuhan.

282
00:13:06,720 --> 00:13:09,580
They might have gone to the countryside for refuge.

283
00:13:09,920 --> 00:13:11,200
I hope so.

284
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:13,640
Wanfu.

285
00:13:13,880 --> 00:13:15,540
If you have hope in your heart,

286
00:13:15,560 --> 00:13:16,960
you will have willpower.

287
00:13:17,040 --> 00:13:18,640
If this willpower is strong,

288
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:20,000
there will definitely be an echo.

289
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:20,960
Compatriots!

290
00:13:21,160 --> 00:13:23,680
The Isogai and Itagaki divisions suffered heavy losses.

291
00:13:23,680 --> 00:13:25,360
China will win!

292
00:13:25,360 --> 00:13:26,600
Look.

293
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:28,720
Just Tai'erzhuang alone

294
00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:32,360
severely damaged the Isogai and Itagaki divisions!

295
00:13:32,960 --> 00:13:35,920
As long as the 400 million compatriots are united,

296
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:38,440
united as one against a common enemy,

297
00:13:38,640 --> 00:13:41,080
the final victory will definitely be ours.

298
00:13:41,560 --> 00:13:43,000
Yes, Master.

299
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:44,920
The Japanese will be driven back to their lair,

300
00:13:44,920 --> 00:13:46,040
that is for sure.

301
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:47,920
But before they go back,

302
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:49,120
you guys,

303
00:13:49,400 --> 00:13:51,860
can't keep living under this bridge, right?

304
00:13:51,920 --> 00:13:53,650
You have to find a place to live.

305
00:13:54,280 --> 00:13:55,120
That's true.

306
00:13:57,120 --> 00:13:58,040
Let me think.

307
00:13:58,520 --> 00:14:00,180
Who else do I know in Shanghai?

308
00:14:01,040 --> 00:14:02,770
Who else has a lot of influence?

309
00:14:07,960 --> 00:14:08,920
Madam.

310
00:14:09,800 --> 00:14:11,480
Our flour-stuffed buns,

311
00:14:11,760 --> 00:14:12,560
weren't they unfinished

312
00:14:12,560 --> 00:14:13,560
when Brother Qi called us away

313
00:14:13,560 --> 00:14:14,760
to pick up Master?

314
00:14:16,640 --> 00:14:17,760
You mean Mr. Tian?

315
00:14:19,400 --> 00:14:21,240
We can try begging him.

316
00:14:21,880 --> 00:14:23,440
But Mr. Tian

317
00:14:23,560 --> 00:14:25,400
is not related to us.

318
00:14:25,920 --> 00:14:27,240
He's already done everything possible

319
00:14:27,240 --> 00:14:28,520
by getting Master out.

320
00:14:28,920 --> 00:14:30,320
We shouldn't keep going to him

321
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:31,320
again and again.

322
00:14:31,880 --> 00:14:33,240
You made a good point.

323
00:14:33,560 --> 00:14:34,840
Not related to us.

324
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:36,280
If he's not related to us,

325
00:14:36,280 --> 00:14:38,760
why would he help us get Master out?

326
00:14:39,320 --> 00:14:40,280
What does this mean?

327
00:14:40,280 --> 00:14:43,240
It means he is a kind and generous person.

328
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:45,040
He is willing to help others.

329
00:14:45,240 --> 00:14:45,840
Whatever.

330
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:47,280
I'll head back to Lutai Restaurant first

331
00:14:47,280 --> 00:14:49,480
to finish making the baozi and bring them to him.

332
00:14:49,480 --> 00:14:50,120
First,

333
00:14:50,280 --> 00:14:52,800
we want to thank him for saving Master.

334
00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:54,240
Second,

335
00:14:54,440 --> 00:14:55,840
we must keep our promise.

336
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:58,320
If we said we'd make baozi for seven days, we will.

337
00:14:58,320 --> 00:14:59,240
Third.

338
00:14:59,920 --> 00:15:01,440
I'll test the waters

339
00:15:01,800 --> 00:15:02,960
and see if he can give us

340
00:15:02,960 --> 00:15:04,240
a place to stay.

341
00:15:07,280 --> 00:15:08,520
Is that appropriate?

342
00:15:09,160 --> 00:15:10,400
Who cares if it's appropriate?

343
00:15:10,400 --> 00:15:11,730
Let's just give it a try.

344
00:15:12,680 --> 00:15:14,040
But let me say this,

345
00:15:14,400 --> 00:15:15,040
Madam.

346
00:15:15,720 --> 00:15:16,760
You and Master

347
00:15:17,040 --> 00:15:18,640
both lived in your own houses

348
00:15:19,160 --> 00:15:21,000
in Nanjing and Shanghai.

349
00:15:21,440 --> 00:15:22,800
If this Mr. Tian

350
00:15:22,840 --> 00:15:24,240
is willing to help us,

351
00:15:24,600 --> 00:15:26,800
you will have to live under someone else's roof.

352
00:15:26,800 --> 00:15:28,060
You need to be prepared

353
00:15:28,400 --> 00:15:30,800
to suffer a bit of grievance.

354
00:15:35,720 --> 00:15:36,800
Wanfu.

355
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:40,960
What does it matter to live under someone else's roof?

356
00:15:41,080 --> 00:15:43,680
Yueming is Yunkui's flesh and blood.

357
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:46,720
Yujiao and I

358
00:15:47,080 --> 00:15:50,410
have a responsibility to protect him so he grows up healthy.

359
00:15:50,760 --> 00:15:51,760
Compared to this,

360
00:15:52,160 --> 00:15:54,280
what does a little grievance matter?

361
00:15:56,480 --> 00:15:57,640
Yujiao.

362
00:15:58,480 --> 00:15:59,600
Right?

363
00:16:03,800 --> 00:16:05,040
You are right.

364
00:16:05,720 --> 00:16:06,250
Alright.

365
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:06,900
Then...

366
00:16:07,080 --> 00:16:08,160
I'll head back to Lutai Restaurant

367
00:16:08,160 --> 00:16:09,220
and make baozi now.

368
00:16:09,760 --> 00:16:10,960
Just wait for me here.

369
00:16:11,040 --> 00:16:11,700
Right here.

370
00:16:11,840 --> 00:16:12,800
I'll be quick.

371
00:16:14,800 --> 00:16:15,600
Be careful.

372
00:16:31,640 --> 00:16:32,080
No, no.

373
00:16:32,200 --> 00:16:33,080
What are you doing?

374
00:16:33,080 --> 00:16:34,880
I'm here to deliver baozi to Mr. Tian.

375
00:16:34,880 --> 00:16:36,560
No one gets in without Qi's permission.

376
00:16:36,560 --> 00:16:37,000
Go.

377
00:16:37,080 --> 00:16:37,760
Listen, brother.

378
00:16:37,760 --> 00:16:38,880
I've been here six times already.

379
00:16:38,880 --> 00:16:41,080
Mr. Tian is talking with Butler Zhu.

380
00:16:41,120 --> 00:16:42,400
Watch what you say when you go up.

381
00:16:42,400 --> 00:16:42,880
Don't make it difficult for me.

382
00:16:42,880 --> 00:16:43,610
Understood.

383
00:16:43,800 --> 00:16:44,400
Qi.

384
00:16:44,640 --> 00:16:45,440
Qi.

385
00:16:46,080 --> 00:16:47,400
It's me, Wanfu.

386
00:16:49,080 --> 00:16:49,680
See?

387
00:16:49,840 --> 00:16:50,520
Qi knows me.

388
00:16:50,680 --> 00:16:51,340
Qi knows me.

389
00:16:51,440 --> 00:16:52,600
Thank you.

390
00:16:54,920 --> 00:16:55,800
Qi.

391
00:16:56,800 --> 00:16:59,200
All right, take them back.

392
00:16:59,680 --> 00:17:00,640
Mr. Tian said

393
00:17:01,040 --> 00:17:02,480
he's eaten your baozi for six days,

394
00:17:02,480 --> 00:17:03,640
and really enjoyed it.

395
00:17:03,640 --> 00:17:04,960
But he's getting sick of it.

396
00:17:04,960 --> 00:17:06,760
Even if you made hazel grouse meat today,

397
00:17:06,760 --> 00:17:07,760
he wouldn't eat it.

398
00:17:07,760 --> 00:17:08,680
Come on, Qi.

399
00:17:08,960 --> 00:17:10,020
I promised Mr. Tian

400
00:17:10,040 --> 00:17:11,079
to bring him baozi for seven days.

401
00:17:11,079 --> 00:17:12,800
It's been six days, just one more left.

402
00:17:12,800 --> 00:17:13,800
And today's batch

403
00:17:13,960 --> 00:17:15,440
is definitely different from before.

404
00:17:15,440 --> 00:17:17,160
Although it's not exotic delicacies,

405
00:17:17,160 --> 00:17:19,200
I promise Mr. Tian will love it.

406
00:17:19,960 --> 00:17:21,599
All right, go back.

407
00:17:23,440 --> 00:17:26,119
Qi, let me tell you the truth.

408
00:17:26,640 --> 00:17:28,400
Delivering the baozi is secondary.

409
00:17:28,400 --> 00:17:29,320
The main thing is that

410
00:17:29,320 --> 00:17:30,040
you and Mr. Tian

411
00:17:30,040 --> 00:17:31,600
have done me a huge favor.

412
00:17:31,960 --> 00:17:33,680
Although I can't thank you enough,

413
00:17:33,680 --> 00:17:34,640
but you and Mr. Tian

414
00:17:34,640 --> 00:17:35,320
truly

415
00:17:35,440 --> 00:17:37,440
saved my family's lives.

416
00:17:37,720 --> 00:17:38,360
I...

417
00:17:38,560 --> 00:17:40,280
If I don't see Mr. Tian,

418
00:17:40,360 --> 00:17:42,160
I'll feel bad about it.

419
00:17:43,560 --> 00:17:43,890
Okay.

420
00:17:44,240 --> 00:17:45,370
Then come up with me.

421
00:17:45,520 --> 00:17:47,400
Thank you, Qi.

422
00:18:05,560 --> 00:18:07,220
Everyone is tired after work.

423
00:18:07,480 --> 00:18:09,160
They all want to hurry back to their rooms and rest.

424
00:18:09,160 --> 00:18:10,080
But him,

425
00:18:10,440 --> 00:18:11,360
standing in the kitchen,

426
00:18:11,360 --> 00:18:12,840
looking through that large window,

427
00:18:12,840 --> 00:18:15,040
staring at your bedroom, Sir,

428
00:18:15,160 --> 00:18:16,320
and the study,

429
00:18:16,600 --> 00:18:18,000
standing there for half a day.

430
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:19,730
I've caught him several times.

431
00:18:20,320 --> 00:18:21,800
Do you think this is normal?

432
00:18:21,800 --> 00:18:23,720
So I found an excuse and fired him.

433
00:18:25,600 --> 00:18:28,280
Then what if I want to eat Double Pepper Fish Head?

434
00:18:28,280 --> 00:18:31,360
Sir, Hunan Cuisine chefs are easy to find.

435
00:18:33,360 --> 00:18:36,490
But a good Cantonese cuisine chef is really hard to find.

436
00:18:36,520 --> 00:18:38,720
I fired the Cantonese cuisine chef too.

437
00:18:39,160 --> 00:18:40,620
He was even more abnormal.

438
00:18:40,800 --> 00:18:42,330
He constantly asked Sibao,

439
00:18:42,680 --> 00:18:45,120
When does Sir go to bed?

440
00:18:45,480 --> 00:18:46,540
When does he go out?

441
00:18:46,760 --> 00:18:48,080
Who does he meet?

442
00:18:48,400 --> 00:18:50,330
Are these things a chef should ask?

443
00:18:50,400 --> 00:18:52,800
So I found an opportunity and fired him too.

444
00:18:53,600 --> 00:18:55,200
Sir, Wanfu, who makes Baozi,

445
00:18:55,320 --> 00:18:57,250
insisted on coming up to thank you.

446
00:18:58,080 --> 00:18:58,680
Mr. Tian.

447
00:18:58,960 --> 00:18:59,880
It's me.

448
00:19:00,200 --> 00:19:01,040
Stop him.

449
00:19:01,360 --> 00:19:03,320
I can't look at those steamer baskets of Baozi right now.

450
00:19:03,320 --> 00:19:03,850
Mr. Tian.

451
00:19:03,960 --> 00:19:05,040
Hurry up, let him go.

452
00:19:05,040 --> 00:19:06,200
Mr. Tian.

453
00:19:06,560 --> 00:19:06,960
Go.

454
00:19:07,440 --> 00:19:08,560
My father was saved.

455
00:19:08,560 --> 00:19:09,820
I came to kowtow to you.

456
00:19:10,000 --> 00:19:11,130
Thank you, Mr. Tian.

457
00:19:11,160 --> 00:19:12,000
Thank you, Mr. Tian.

458
00:19:12,000 --> 00:19:13,320
Okay, I know.

459
00:19:13,360 --> 00:19:14,760
Go away and take the Baozi with you.

460
00:19:14,760 --> 00:19:15,800
I can't look at them right now.

461
00:19:15,800 --> 00:19:16,200
Let's go.

462
00:19:16,200 --> 00:19:17,000
No, Mr. Tian.

463
00:19:17,120 --> 00:19:17,360
Hurry.

464
00:19:17,360 --> 00:19:18,920
I promised to make Baozi for you for seven days.

465
00:19:18,920 --> 00:19:20,720
I must keep my word, Mr. Tian.

466
00:19:20,800 --> 00:19:22,560
I was already sick of eating them by the fifth day.

467
00:19:22,560 --> 00:19:23,280
Take them away quickly.

468
00:19:23,280 --> 00:19:25,210
But today's filling is different.

469
00:19:25,280 --> 00:19:26,610
I won't eat any filling.

470
00:19:26,640 --> 00:19:27,170
Mr. Tian.

471
00:19:27,240 --> 00:19:29,440
Today I made flour-filled ones for you.

472
00:19:44,720 --> 00:19:45,800
Flour-filled?

473
00:19:46,840 --> 00:19:48,500
Isn't that just a steamed bun?

474
00:19:49,720 --> 00:19:50,720
Mr. Tian.

475
00:19:51,880 --> 00:19:53,840
Actually, when I was making Baozi for you,

476
00:19:53,840 --> 00:19:54,840
by the sixth day,

477
00:19:55,520 --> 00:19:57,480
I didn't know what filling to make anymore.

478
00:19:57,480 --> 00:19:59,400
But I said seven kinds of Baozi,

479
00:19:59,520 --> 00:20:00,240
so it must be seven kinds.

480
00:20:00,240 --> 00:20:01,440
I have to keep my word.

481
00:20:01,520 --> 00:20:02,320
So I thought,

482
00:20:02,760 --> 00:20:04,090
I might as well honestly

483
00:20:04,480 --> 00:20:06,540
make a basket of steamed buns for you.

484
00:20:30,800 --> 00:20:31,800
Actually,

485
00:20:33,000 --> 00:20:36,280
what I told you before about the Seven Delicacies of Lanling

486
00:20:36,280 --> 00:20:37,840
was also nonsense.

487
00:20:38,200 --> 00:20:39,330
But I can guarantee,

488
00:20:39,600 --> 00:20:41,960
the previous six fillings were all made with heart.

489
00:20:41,960 --> 00:20:43,760
Including today's basket of steamed buns,

490
00:20:43,760 --> 00:20:45,420
I also made them with my heart.

491
00:20:45,800 --> 00:20:47,200
I just want to thank you.

492
00:20:48,080 --> 00:20:49,610
You saved my father's life.

493
00:20:51,760 --> 00:20:54,320
Do you know why I helped you?

494
00:20:55,920 --> 00:20:58,360
It's not because I like your baozi filling.

495
00:20:58,840 --> 00:21:01,760
I like the taste of the dough.

496
00:21:02,520 --> 00:21:03,960
I'm from Shandong.

497
00:21:05,160 --> 00:21:06,420
Shandong steamed buns

498
00:21:07,080 --> 00:21:08,240
taste just like my childhood.

499
00:21:08,240 --> 00:21:09,040
Yes, yes, yes.

500
00:21:09,280 --> 00:21:11,880
This is the traditional recipe from my hometown, Lanling.

501
00:21:11,880 --> 00:21:13,480
Hard-kneaded steamed buns.

502
00:21:13,600 --> 00:21:16,200
Every family's steamed buns taste different.

503
00:21:16,200 --> 00:21:17,240
The ones you steam

504
00:21:17,600 --> 00:21:19,000
have a hint of sweetness.

505
00:21:19,280 --> 00:21:20,610
They're very fragrant.

506
00:21:21,520 --> 00:21:23,650
It's the taste of my mother's cooking.

507
00:21:24,360 --> 00:21:26,360
Thank you for liking them, Mr. Tian.

508
00:21:26,720 --> 00:21:29,000
Sir, let's not just eat them plain.

509
00:21:29,120 --> 00:21:31,180
I'll get you some dishes to go with it.

510
00:21:33,480 --> 00:21:34,400
Wanfu.

511
00:21:35,920 --> 00:21:37,200
Besides making baozi

512
00:21:37,520 --> 00:21:38,800
and steamed buns,

513
00:21:39,200 --> 00:21:40,600
what other Shandong dishes can you cook?

514
00:21:40,600 --> 00:21:41,280
Yes.

515
00:21:41,520 --> 00:21:42,920
I can basically cook all of them.

516
00:21:42,920 --> 00:21:44,000
Back at Lutai Restaurant,

517
00:21:44,000 --> 00:21:45,360
I was the top chef for Shandong cuisine.

518
00:21:45,360 --> 00:21:46,690
Do you want to stay here?

519
00:21:48,240 --> 00:21:48,800
Stay?

520
00:21:49,400 --> 00:21:51,760
Stay and be your chef?

521
00:21:53,880 --> 00:21:55,680
But my current boss

522
00:21:56,040 --> 00:21:57,170
treats me very well.

523
00:21:57,360 --> 00:21:57,920
I

524
00:21:58,080 --> 00:21:59,560
shouldn't let him down.

525
00:22:02,120 --> 00:22:02,920
Got it.

526
00:22:03,880 --> 00:22:05,080
Pretend I didn't ask.

527
00:22:09,760 --> 00:22:10,290
Let's go.

528
00:22:10,360 --> 00:22:11,000
No, no, no.

529
00:22:11,280 --> 00:22:13,010
Mr. Tian, if I become your chef,

530
00:22:13,720 --> 00:22:15,050
is there a place to live?

531
00:22:15,400 --> 00:22:16,200
Nonsense.

532
00:22:16,440 --> 00:22:17,760
The row of cabins behind this building

533
00:22:17,760 --> 00:22:19,000
is for the servants, isn't it?

534
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:19,960
But...

535
00:22:20,120 --> 00:22:22,440
I also have a wife and a child.

536
00:22:22,520 --> 00:22:23,880
How is that going to work?

537
00:22:23,880 --> 00:22:24,800
How many wives?

538
00:22:24,880 --> 00:22:25,720
O-One.

539
00:22:25,840 --> 00:22:26,720
Only one.

540
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:27,880
But

541
00:22:28,040 --> 00:22:29,600
I also have an old father.

542
00:22:29,800 --> 00:22:30,720
Are you done?

543
00:22:31,000 --> 00:22:32,520
What do you think Tian Mansion is?

544
00:22:32,520 --> 00:22:33,160
Go, go.

545
00:22:33,400 --> 00:22:33,960
Go.

546
00:22:34,000 --> 00:22:34,760
Is it that old man

547
00:22:34,760 --> 00:22:36,600
who refused to read the apology letter?

548
00:22:36,600 --> 00:22:37,240
Yes.

549
00:22:37,440 --> 00:22:38,280
He's your father?

550
00:22:38,280 --> 00:22:39,040
My father.

551
00:22:39,760 --> 00:22:41,200
Isn't his surname Zhang?

552
00:22:42,640 --> 00:22:44,120
I'm not his biological son.

553
00:22:44,120 --> 00:22:45,120
He adopted me.

554
00:22:45,400 --> 00:22:45,800
But

555
00:22:46,080 --> 00:22:47,480
we are closer than blood.

556
00:22:47,880 --> 00:22:48,800
Mr. Tian.

557
00:22:49,160 --> 00:22:50,680
My father is very sick now.

558
00:22:51,000 --> 00:22:52,530
And we have nowhere to live.

559
00:22:52,600 --> 00:22:53,360
If you, Mr. Tian,

560
00:22:53,360 --> 00:22:55,360
are willing to give us a place to live,

561
00:22:55,360 --> 00:22:56,720
I'm willing to cook for you every day.

562
00:22:56,720 --> 00:22:58,520
I'll cook all kinds of Shandong dishes for you.

563
00:22:58,520 --> 00:22:59,840
And I won't even take any wages.

564
00:22:59,840 --> 00:23:00,800
Why

565
00:23:01,800 --> 00:23:04,200
would I eat your food and not pay you?

566
00:23:06,680 --> 00:23:08,080
Keep an eye on your child.

567
00:23:08,400 --> 00:23:09,800
Don't let him run around.

568
00:23:12,640 --> 00:23:13,840
Thank you, Mr. Tian.

569
00:23:14,320 --> 00:23:15,250
He can't run yet.

570
00:23:15,440 --> 00:23:16,480
He can only be held.

571
00:23:16,480 --> 00:23:17,680
Thank you. Thank you.

572
00:23:18,920 --> 00:23:19,850
Let's go, Wanfu.

573
00:23:20,520 --> 00:23:22,120
Thank you, Mr. Tian.

574
00:23:26,160 --> 00:23:28,120
Sir, as soon as you asked,

575
00:23:28,200 --> 00:23:29,480
four people came.

576
00:23:29,760 --> 00:23:30,960
What are their backgrounds?

577
00:23:30,960 --> 00:23:32,400
We haven't investigated them at all.

578
00:23:32,400 --> 00:23:34,400
Shouldn't we be more careful?

579
00:23:34,880 --> 00:23:37,120
Can you make this Shandong steamed bun?

580
00:23:37,920 --> 00:23:38,840
No.

581
00:23:42,560 --> 00:23:43,890
Pour me a glass of water.

582
00:23:47,440 --> 00:23:48,200
Sibao,

583
00:23:48,560 --> 00:23:49,760
serve a glass of water.

584
00:23:49,760 --> 00:23:50,400
Yes, sir.

585
00:23:57,880 --> 00:23:59,080
Sir, water.

586
00:23:59,360 --> 00:24:00,000
Forget it.

587
00:24:00,400 --> 00:24:03,200
Eating steamed buns with water makes you too full.

588
00:24:17,880 --> 00:24:19,340
Come back and visit often.

589
00:24:21,480 --> 00:24:22,200
Manager,

590
00:24:22,640 --> 00:24:24,720
this is the money I owe for the baozi.

591
00:24:25,040 --> 00:24:26,640
You usually say I'm stingy.

592
00:24:26,800 --> 00:24:29,240
That's business. We have to budget carefully.

593
00:24:29,240 --> 00:24:31,000
But I can't take this money.

594
00:24:31,760 --> 00:24:34,420
This is the money you use to save someone's life.

595
00:24:34,560 --> 00:24:36,400
It is better than building a seven-story pagoda.

596
00:24:36,400 --> 00:24:37,200
I understand.

597
00:24:37,480 --> 00:24:38,720
Count me in.

598
00:24:41,200 --> 00:24:41,930
Absolutely.

599
00:24:42,160 --> 00:24:42,960
Kid,

600
00:24:43,320 --> 00:24:45,780
if you're not happy working for the new boss,

601
00:24:45,880 --> 00:24:46,560
come back.

602
00:24:47,080 --> 00:24:48,410
This is still your home.

603
00:24:57,400 --> 00:24:58,360
Brother.

604
00:24:59,400 --> 00:25:00,480
Hold it in.

605
00:25:01,600 --> 00:25:02,530
I'm telling you,

606
00:25:02,880 --> 00:25:05,880
if I see you messing around in the dance hall again,

607
00:25:05,920 --> 00:25:07,240
I'll break your legs.

608
00:25:08,440 --> 00:25:10,280
Look how good Mr. Xu is to us.

609
00:25:11,080 --> 00:25:12,740
Work hard and save some money.

610
00:25:16,640 --> 00:25:17,680
I'm leaving.

611
00:25:20,720 --> 00:25:21,800
Brother.

612
00:25:24,920 --> 00:25:25,980
Why are you crying?

613
00:25:26,480 --> 00:25:27,480
Are you mourning?

614
00:25:27,840 --> 00:25:29,640
If you cry again, I'll tear your mouth.

615
00:25:29,640 --> 00:25:30,800
I'm not dead.

616
00:25:31,480 --> 00:25:33,010
I'm just in the concession.

617
00:25:33,120 --> 00:25:35,320
I'll come back and see you when I'm free.

618
00:25:36,760 --> 00:25:37,490
I'm leaving.

619
00:25:40,400 --> 00:25:43,200
Brother, come back often.

620
00:25:51,120 --> 00:25:52,080
Qi, Qi.

621
00:25:59,480 --> 00:26:00,280
Sibao,

622
00:26:00,760 --> 00:26:01,640
Xiaodouzi.

623
00:26:09,440 --> 00:26:11,440
This is the new lad, Meng Wanfu.

624
00:26:12,000 --> 00:26:12,520
Wanfu.

625
00:26:13,600 --> 00:26:14,480
Hello, hello.

626
00:26:16,880 --> 00:26:18,160
Old man, Mrs. Meng,

627
00:26:18,480 --> 00:26:20,280
this is the servants' quarters.

628
00:26:20,320 --> 00:26:22,240
The innermost room is yours.

629
00:26:22,920 --> 00:26:25,040
This whole area is the back kitchen.

630
00:26:25,720 --> 00:26:26,800
Chef Jiao.

631
00:26:27,760 --> 00:26:28,360
Qi.

632
00:26:31,880 --> 00:26:32,360
Hello, Chef Jiao.

633
00:26:32,360 --> 00:26:33,360
Hello, Chef Jiao.

634
00:26:34,400 --> 00:26:35,200
Are you busy, Qi?

635
00:26:35,200 --> 00:26:36,040
Chef Jiao,

636
00:26:36,400 --> 00:26:38,840
this is the new Shandong cuisine chef hired by Mr. Tian,

637
00:26:38,840 --> 00:26:39,640
Meng Wanfu.

638
00:26:40,680 --> 00:26:41,880
Hello, Chef Jiao.

639
00:26:43,040 --> 00:26:43,680
Nice to meet you.

640
00:26:43,680 --> 00:26:45,410
Chef Jiao is our head chef here.

641
00:26:46,240 --> 00:26:47,770
Then Chef Jiao is my senior.

642
00:26:47,800 --> 00:26:49,920
I'm just here to be your assistant.

643
00:26:50,960 --> 00:26:51,960
Glad to hear that.

644
00:26:52,440 --> 00:26:54,960
From now on, if Mr. Tian orders Shandong cuisine,

645
00:26:54,960 --> 00:26:55,760
you will cook.

646
00:26:56,240 --> 00:26:57,900
But everything in the kitchen

647
00:26:58,040 --> 00:26:59,960
is managed by Chef Jiao.

648
00:27:00,120 --> 00:27:01,850
The order cannot be disrupted.

649
00:27:01,920 --> 00:27:03,080
Of course.

650
00:27:03,360 --> 00:27:04,320
First come, first served.

651
00:27:04,320 --> 00:27:05,600
I know that.

652
00:27:05,760 --> 00:27:08,240
Chef Jiao, please take care of us from now on.

653
00:27:08,720 --> 00:27:10,120
I wouldn't say take care.

654
00:27:10,160 --> 00:27:12,120
Lad, you are lucky.

655
00:27:12,360 --> 00:27:14,800
Mr. Tian favors you so much

656
00:27:15,080 --> 00:27:16,680
that you could bring your whole family.

657
00:27:16,680 --> 00:27:18,640
I've been with Mr. Tian for so many years

658
00:27:18,640 --> 00:27:20,700
and I don't even have this privilege.

659
00:27:20,960 --> 00:27:22,360
Mr. Tian is generous to his subordinates.

660
00:27:22,360 --> 00:27:23,420
It's all arranged.

661
00:27:23,800 --> 00:27:25,000
Qi is right.

662
00:27:25,920 --> 00:27:27,760
Finally, when you are not on duty,

663
00:27:27,760 --> 00:27:29,400
you can stay in this small garden

664
00:27:29,400 --> 00:27:30,040
to rest

665
00:27:30,320 --> 00:27:31,000
and relax.

666
00:27:31,200 --> 00:27:32,530
But when you are on duty,

667
00:27:32,920 --> 00:27:34,640
you must do your duty.

668
00:27:34,800 --> 00:27:36,000
Look at what you should look at,

669
00:27:36,000 --> 00:27:38,000
and don't look at what you shouldn't.

670
00:27:38,000 --> 00:27:39,330
Say what you should say,

671
00:27:39,360 --> 00:27:41,200
and don't say what you shouldn't.

672
00:27:41,200 --> 00:27:42,320
Go where you should go,

673
00:27:42,320 --> 00:27:44,180
and don't go where you shouldn't.

674
00:27:44,360 --> 00:27:45,890
The rules cannot be broken.

675
00:27:46,640 --> 00:27:47,480
Qi.

676
00:27:48,040 --> 00:27:50,000
We are an innocent

677
00:27:50,320 --> 00:27:52,240
family who keep our hands clean.

678
00:27:52,840 --> 00:27:53,440
Yes.

679
00:27:53,800 --> 00:27:54,080
Yes.

680
00:27:54,280 --> 00:27:55,320
Don't worry, Qi.

681
00:27:55,560 --> 00:27:56,480
I've remembered it all.

682
00:27:56,480 --> 00:27:57,940
There will be no mistakes.

683
00:27:59,640 --> 00:28:00,480
Four Treasures, Douzi,

684
00:28:00,480 --> 00:28:01,680
help Wanfu settle in.

685
00:28:01,880 --> 00:28:02,600
Yes.

686
00:28:02,840 --> 00:28:03,880
I'll go report to Mr. Tian.

687
00:28:03,880 --> 00:28:04,210
Okay.

688
00:28:04,360 --> 00:28:05,400
Go ahead, Qi.

689
00:28:05,520 --> 00:28:06,160
Take care.

690
00:28:06,800 --> 00:28:07,880
Thank you, Qi.

691
00:28:10,280 --> 00:28:11,140
Brother Wanfu.

692
00:28:12,120 --> 00:28:12,980
Thank you, Lad.

693
00:28:13,120 --> 00:28:13,600
Thanks.

694
00:28:14,200 --> 00:28:15,000
Here, give this to me.

695
00:28:15,000 --> 00:28:15,440
Douzi.

696
00:28:16,000 --> 00:28:17,400
The Soft-Stirred Eel I asked you to prepare,

697
00:28:17,400 --> 00:28:18,600
did you do it?

698
00:28:19,080 --> 00:28:20,010
Four Treasures.

699
00:28:20,200 --> 00:28:22,800
Have you sorted out the Three Whites of Taihu Lake?

700
00:28:22,800 --> 00:28:24,760
Don't delay Mr. Tian's meal.

701
00:28:25,280 --> 00:28:26,140
These two kids.

702
00:28:26,600 --> 00:28:27,200
Yes.

703
00:28:27,320 --> 00:28:28,480
Well, Lad,

704
00:28:28,560 --> 00:28:29,760
you go do your work.

705
00:28:29,880 --> 00:28:31,140
I can settle in myself.

706
00:28:31,200 --> 00:28:31,840
Go ahead.

707
00:28:31,920 --> 00:28:32,640
Go ahead.

708
00:28:32,760 --> 00:28:33,160
Go ahead.

709
00:28:33,160 --> 00:28:35,020
Alright, don't just stand there.

710
00:28:35,120 --> 00:28:36,520
You don't know the rules.

711
00:28:41,840 --> 00:28:43,280
Chef Meng, I'm sorry.

712
00:28:43,640 --> 00:28:44,760
Mr. Tian is strict.

713
00:28:44,960 --> 00:28:46,440
These kids are too young

714
00:28:46,560 --> 00:28:47,760
and lack discipline.

715
00:28:47,920 --> 00:28:49,200
I have to teach them properly.

716
00:28:49,200 --> 00:28:49,720
Yes.

717
00:28:49,880 --> 00:28:52,340
Then let's exchange what we have privately.

718
00:28:52,960 --> 00:28:54,520
You guys go ahead.

719
00:28:55,760 --> 00:28:57,240
Chef Jiao, go ahead.

720
00:29:04,640 --> 00:29:05,240
Master,

721
00:29:05,680 --> 00:29:06,940
let's go inside first.

722
00:29:07,160 --> 00:29:07,690
Let's go.

723
00:29:07,720 --> 00:29:08,680
It seems to be that one.

724
00:29:08,680 --> 00:29:09,520
Let's go.

725
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:18,330
This should be the room.

726
00:29:30,040 --> 00:29:30,640
It's fine.

727
00:29:30,680 --> 00:29:32,120
I'll fix it.

728
00:29:55,520 --> 00:29:56,840
This room is so small.

729
00:29:57,040 --> 00:29:58,840
How can the three of us live here?

730
00:29:58,920 --> 00:30:00,440
It is a bit small.

731
00:30:02,080 --> 00:30:04,400
But it'll be warm if we squeeze together.

732
00:30:05,040 --> 00:30:06,200
It's quite good.

733
00:30:07,480 --> 00:30:08,740
And there are windows.

734
00:30:25,960 --> 00:30:26,880
In the past,

735
00:30:27,440 --> 00:30:28,900
I've slept under a bridge.

736
00:30:29,080 --> 00:30:30,880
I've also slept next to a boiler.

737
00:30:31,280 --> 00:30:32,280
Anyway, this room

738
00:30:32,480 --> 00:30:35,280
is much more comfortable than where I used to live.

739
00:30:36,200 --> 00:30:38,160
Don't worry, I have an idea.

740
00:30:57,760 --> 00:30:59,960
You two, please come in.

741
00:31:00,120 --> 00:31:01,840
Welcome to Villa No. 2.

742
00:31:02,160 --> 00:31:03,240
Kicking Li Shuyuan,

743
00:31:03,240 --> 00:31:05,240
punching Zhang Yunqi.

744
00:31:07,080 --> 00:31:07,880
Sir, Madam,

745
00:31:08,160 --> 00:31:09,360
please look this way.

746
00:31:09,680 --> 00:31:10,280
This

747
00:31:10,480 --> 00:31:13,000
is the best-lit place in the whole house.

748
00:31:13,680 --> 00:31:15,200
This, of course, is Madam

749
00:31:15,560 --> 00:31:17,640
and little Yueming's bedroom.

750
00:31:18,600 --> 00:31:20,360
Since children need to grow fast,

751
00:31:20,360 --> 00:31:21,760
they need more sunshine.

752
00:31:22,080 --> 00:31:23,200
At night...

753
00:31:32,920 --> 00:31:33,600
Look.

754
00:31:33,720 --> 00:31:34,320
At night,

755
00:31:34,400 --> 00:31:35,930
once this curtain is drawn,

756
00:31:35,960 --> 00:31:37,240
Madam and little Yueming

757
00:31:37,240 --> 00:31:39,640
will have their own private space.

758
00:31:39,720 --> 00:31:40,450
How about it?

759
00:31:41,640 --> 00:31:42,560
Then...

760
00:31:43,000 --> 00:31:44,040
Where do I sleep?

761
00:31:44,200 --> 00:31:46,930
Am I going to squeeze into this small bed with you?

762
00:31:48,200 --> 00:31:50,240
Master, even if you are willing to sleep with me,

763
00:31:50,240 --> 00:31:52,040
I'm not willing to squeeze with you.

764
00:31:52,040 --> 00:31:53,370
I'm not willing either.

765
00:31:53,640 --> 00:31:54,840
Don't worry.

766
00:31:55,240 --> 00:31:56,920
Sir, please step over here.

767
00:31:57,120 --> 00:31:58,320
Please look this way.

768
00:31:59,080 --> 00:31:59,840
Look.

769
00:32:00,120 --> 00:32:01,360
This direction here

770
00:32:01,600 --> 00:32:04,600
is the second best-lit place in the whole house.

771
00:32:04,800 --> 00:32:06,040
Even though it's the second best,

772
00:32:06,040 --> 00:32:06,720
look here,

773
00:32:06,960 --> 00:32:08,320
it has big windows.

774
00:32:08,520 --> 00:32:09,450
Also, look here.

775
00:32:09,920 --> 00:32:12,040
There is plenty of space to move around.

776
00:32:12,040 --> 00:32:14,080
So this excellent spot

777
00:32:14,200 --> 00:32:16,280
is, of course, your bedroom, Master.

778
00:32:17,160 --> 00:32:18,320
I sleep on the floor?

779
00:32:18,400 --> 00:32:20,360
How could I let you sleep on the floor?

780
00:32:20,360 --> 00:32:22,640
Madam, could you please use your delicate hands

781
00:32:22,640 --> 00:32:24,040
to help me lift the table?

782
00:32:26,240 --> 00:32:28,320
Just a little bit this way.

783
00:32:29,440 --> 00:32:29,960
Master,

784
00:32:30,120 --> 00:32:33,280
please move over a little.

785
00:32:34,000 --> 00:32:34,520
Okay.

786
00:32:35,080 --> 00:32:37,120
I'll show you a magic trick.

787
00:32:49,760 --> 00:32:51,480
Master, this is your bed.

788
00:32:51,760 --> 00:32:52,560
There's more.

789
00:33:03,480 --> 00:33:06,040
Master, once this curtain is drawn,

790
00:33:06,080 --> 00:33:08,410
all three of us will have our own bedrooms.

791
00:33:09,960 --> 00:33:11,400
Good, good, good.

792
00:33:11,600 --> 00:33:15,440
A bamboo dish of rice, a single gourd of drink, in a mean alley.

793
00:33:15,800 --> 00:33:17,720
Others could not have endured such hardship.

794
00:33:17,720 --> 00:33:20,520
Father, how about you move over a little bit again.

795
00:33:20,640 --> 00:33:21,240
Okay.

796
00:33:22,360 --> 00:33:24,440
Yet Hui did not change his joy.

797
00:33:24,880 --> 00:33:25,480
Okay.

798
00:33:25,800 --> 00:33:27,000
Good, good, good.

799
00:33:27,160 --> 00:33:27,800
Okay.

800
00:33:29,600 --> 00:33:30,360
Wanfu.

801
00:33:31,120 --> 00:33:33,080
You only left such a small space for yourself,

802
00:33:33,080 --> 00:33:34,480
isn't it too cramped?

803
00:33:36,760 --> 00:33:37,600
Madam, look.

804
00:33:37,720 --> 00:33:39,120
This window faces

805
00:33:39,160 --> 00:33:40,440
our kitchen's back door.

806
00:33:40,440 --> 00:33:42,640
I can see at a glance if anyone steals vegetables.

807
00:33:42,640 --> 00:33:43,800
And that Chef Jiao.

808
00:33:44,000 --> 00:33:45,840
How dare he bring his pot

809
00:33:45,920 --> 00:33:47,680
and come here to set rules for us.

810
00:33:47,680 --> 00:33:48,760
Before he even stepped inside,

811
00:33:48,760 --> 00:33:50,520
I chased him out with a stick.

812
00:33:51,000 --> 00:33:53,640
With me guarding the door, you can rest assured.

813
00:33:53,640 --> 00:33:54,640
Wanfu.

814
00:33:55,880 --> 00:33:56,640
Thank you.

815
00:33:57,880 --> 00:33:59,960
Madam, please don't say that.

816
00:34:00,920 --> 00:34:02,760
Actually, letting you live here,

817
00:34:02,760 --> 00:34:04,520
I feel I've wronged you.

818
00:34:05,200 --> 00:34:07,520
The bridal chamber I had with Xiaoyue before

819
00:34:07,520 --> 00:34:09,040
was even smaller than this.

820
00:34:09,040 --> 00:34:11,159
But our Xiaoyue thought of a way.

821
00:34:11,440 --> 00:34:13,500
She added a bedboard to my single bed,

822
00:34:13,560 --> 00:34:15,320
and made folding legs for it.

823
00:34:15,320 --> 00:34:18,480
The single bed instantly became a double bed.

824
00:34:19,120 --> 00:34:20,239
I didn't expect that

825
00:34:20,239 --> 00:34:21,960
after it was bombed during the August 13th Incident,

826
00:34:21,960 --> 00:34:24,120
this skill would be used here.

827
00:34:26,199 --> 00:34:28,159
There are still so many things unpacked.

828
00:34:28,159 --> 00:34:29,199
Madam, madam, madam.

829
00:34:29,199 --> 00:34:30,639
Let's not unpack anymore.

830
00:34:30,639 --> 00:34:32,600
We can do it tomorrow when we wake up.

831
00:34:32,600 --> 00:34:34,440
Everyone is exhausted from the hustle today.

832
00:34:34,440 --> 00:34:36,560
How about we all rest?

833
00:34:37,320 --> 00:34:38,360
Let's rest.

834
00:34:38,600 --> 00:34:40,239
Okay, let's rest.

835
00:34:40,320 --> 00:34:40,960
Resting.

836
00:34:41,199 --> 00:34:41,600
Okay.

837
00:34:41,840 --> 00:34:42,600
Master.

838
00:34:42,840 --> 00:34:45,760
I'll close the curtains for you.

839
00:34:49,040 --> 00:34:51,360
Father, sweet dreams.

840
00:34:51,679 --> 00:34:52,800
Sweet dreams.

841
00:35:03,040 --> 00:35:03,970
Let's rest then.

842
00:35:04,760 --> 00:35:05,440
Rest.

843
00:35:05,640 --> 00:35:06,640
Then Madam, I'll turn off the light.

844
00:35:06,640 --> 00:35:07,320
Okay.

845
00:35:12,880 --> 00:35:14,640
Master, let me use your cane.

846
00:35:26,280 --> 00:35:27,200
Turned off.

847
00:35:35,520 --> 00:35:37,640
Do you have to turn off the light like this every day, Wanfu?

848
00:35:37,640 --> 00:35:38,240
No, Madam.

849
00:35:38,320 --> 00:35:39,200
I just don't know how to fix it.

850
00:35:39,200 --> 00:35:41,120
I'll find an electrician to fix it tomorrow.

851
00:35:41,120 --> 00:35:42,320
Rest assured, Madam.

852
00:35:43,840 --> 00:35:45,640
Master, I'll put it here for you.

853
00:35:45,920 --> 00:35:46,880
Rest early.

854
00:36:19,960 --> 00:36:21,820
Hot dry noodles. Hot dry noodles.

855
00:36:22,600 --> 00:36:24,200
What fragrant sesame paste.

856
00:36:24,400 --> 00:36:25,400
Hot dry noodles.

857
00:36:48,720 --> 00:36:49,280
Sorry, Sir.

858
00:36:49,280 --> 00:36:50,920
I can't salute wearing a long gown.

859
00:36:50,920 --> 00:36:51,800
Yunkui.

860
00:36:52,120 --> 00:36:54,120
No need for formalities between us.

861
00:36:57,120 --> 00:36:58,250
You've been in Wuhan

862
00:36:58,840 --> 00:37:00,240
for a few days now, right?

863
00:37:01,400 --> 00:37:02,530
All your materials,

864
00:37:03,120 --> 00:37:04,380
we have received them.

865
00:37:04,880 --> 00:37:07,440
And in the long letter Lu Yun wrote to me,

866
00:37:07,760 --> 00:37:10,040
he also described the situation at that time in detail,

867
00:37:10,040 --> 00:37:13,360
which is completely consistent with the materials you provided.

868
00:37:13,360 --> 00:37:15,290
The matter is of great importance.

869
00:37:17,000 --> 00:37:17,680
Come.

870
00:37:19,360 --> 00:37:20,820
Let's sit inside and talk.

871
00:37:22,480 --> 00:37:23,920
I have already forwarded all your materials

872
00:37:23,920 --> 00:37:25,360
to Minister He.

873
00:37:26,120 --> 00:37:27,800
After Minister He finished reading them overnight,

874
00:37:27,800 --> 00:37:29,160
he immediately sent a telegraph

875
00:37:29,160 --> 00:37:32,320
to Liao Fengnian, former deputy commander of the 187th Division.

876
00:37:32,320 --> 00:37:32,960
Come, sit.

877
00:37:33,680 --> 00:37:34,680
Sit.

878
00:37:38,040 --> 00:37:40,280
Liao Fengnian was slightly injured before.

879
00:37:40,280 --> 00:37:41,320
From the hospital,

880
00:37:41,320 --> 00:37:43,720
he gave us a detailed report over the phone,

881
00:37:44,360 --> 00:37:45,960
which lasted for a full hour.

882
00:37:47,040 --> 00:37:48,300
After investigation,

883
00:37:48,360 --> 00:37:49,920
Minister He and I agree that

884
00:37:50,400 --> 00:37:52,040
during the Battle of Shanghai,

885
00:37:52,040 --> 00:37:54,680
you strictly followed orders.

886
00:37:55,200 --> 00:37:57,440
You personally led the soldiers of the 87th Brigade

887
00:37:57,440 --> 00:37:58,560
to hold the position

888
00:37:58,560 --> 00:38:00,440
until you were out of ammunition and food.

889
00:38:00,440 --> 00:38:01,720
The so-called...

890
00:38:04,280 --> 00:38:05,840
so-called runaway general

891
00:38:06,160 --> 00:38:07,400
who feared the enemy and abandoned his post

892
00:38:07,400 --> 00:38:10,040
is purely fictitious. You took the blame for others.

893
00:38:10,040 --> 00:38:10,700
Therefore,

894
00:38:10,840 --> 00:38:13,560
you should be fully exonerated and reinstated.

895
00:38:16,800 --> 00:38:17,840
Yunkui,

896
00:38:18,320 --> 00:38:19,600
you have been wronged.

897
00:38:22,720 --> 00:38:23,400
Sir,

898
00:38:23,680 --> 00:38:25,440
thank you for clearing the names of the brothers of the 87th Brigade.

899
00:38:25,440 --> 00:38:26,360
Thank you.

900
00:38:28,240 --> 00:38:29,200
Yunkui,

901
00:38:30,680 --> 00:38:31,880
I'm not finished yet.

902
00:38:33,280 --> 00:38:34,320
Have a seat.

903
00:38:42,520 --> 00:38:43,560
Please sit.

904
00:38:55,080 --> 00:38:56,120
Yunkui,

905
00:38:56,640 --> 00:38:58,600
I know you've been standing at the gate of the Ministry of War

906
00:38:58,600 --> 00:38:59,760
for a few days.

907
00:39:00,480 --> 00:39:02,810
If these materials of yours are reported,

908
00:39:02,880 --> 00:39:03,920
I can imagine

909
00:39:04,240 --> 00:39:06,040
what kind of shock it will cause.

910
00:39:06,320 --> 00:39:07,780
So I invited you here today

911
00:39:08,520 --> 00:39:09,960
as an old friend

912
00:39:10,440 --> 00:39:11,600
and a teacher,

913
00:39:13,080 --> 00:39:15,280
to have a heart-to-heart talk with you.

914
00:39:15,840 --> 00:39:18,320
If we make the announcement as I just said,

915
00:39:18,600 --> 00:39:19,280
then

916
00:39:19,600 --> 00:39:21,860
we also have to deal with another person.

917
00:39:22,440 --> 00:39:24,320
The former commander of the 130th Army's

918
00:39:24,320 --> 00:39:27,480
Infantry 187th Division, Sun Huaiyi.

919
00:39:28,080 --> 00:39:31,010
The charges are improper deployment, poor command,

920
00:39:31,280 --> 00:39:33,520
lying about the military situation after the battle, shirking responsibility,

921
00:39:33,520 --> 00:39:34,720
framing colleagues,

922
00:39:34,720 --> 00:39:36,360
and even killing someone to silence them.

923
00:39:36,360 --> 00:39:37,490
These are all facts.

924
00:39:38,080 --> 00:39:40,610
Is there any problem, Deputy Minister Huang?

925
00:39:41,280 --> 00:39:42,160
Yunkui,

926
00:39:42,720 --> 00:39:43,780
these past few days

927
00:39:44,800 --> 00:39:46,600
you've been hiding everywhere.

928
00:39:46,960 --> 00:39:49,520
I'm afraid you don't know much about the battle situation.

929
00:39:49,520 --> 00:39:54,080
Right now, the Japanese Army is gradually reinforcing East China.

930
00:39:54,680 --> 00:39:56,760
Both sides are locked in a seesaw battle.

931
00:39:56,760 --> 00:39:59,720
The Fifth War Area has decided to abandon Xuzhou.

932
00:39:59,960 --> 00:40:01,320
The battle in Xuzhou is in a stalemate.

933
00:40:01,320 --> 00:40:02,880
To preserve our strength for a long-term war,

934
00:40:02,880 --> 00:40:03,600
retreating

935
00:40:03,800 --> 00:40:05,080
is expected.

936
00:40:05,400 --> 00:40:08,040
General Li Zongren led the armies

937
00:40:08,680 --> 00:40:11,240
to break out towards the Mountainous Area of Henan and Anhui.

938
00:40:11,240 --> 00:40:12,920
He ordered Sun Huaiyi's troops

939
00:40:12,920 --> 00:40:16,400
to bring up the rear and intercept the 9th Division of the Japanese Army.

940
00:40:16,400 --> 00:40:17,260
Three days ago,

941
00:40:17,560 --> 00:40:19,400
all the armies had completely withdrawn.

942
00:40:19,400 --> 00:40:20,360
Sun Huaiyi's troops

943
00:40:20,360 --> 00:40:22,280
then retreated to Huangchuan under the cover of night.

944
00:40:22,280 --> 00:40:24,800
While passing through Xuejiaji in Su County,

945
00:40:24,800 --> 00:40:27,060
they were ambushed by the Japanese Army.

946
00:40:27,280 --> 00:40:28,160
And then?

947
00:40:28,520 --> 00:40:30,400
Because it was a small group of the Japanese Army,

948
00:40:30,400 --> 00:40:32,640
casualties at the Army Headquarters were not heavy.

949
00:40:32,640 --> 00:40:33,920
But unfortunately,

950
00:40:35,080 --> 00:40:37,210
Commander Sun was shot in the abdomen.

951
00:40:37,840 --> 00:40:39,320
He couldn't be saved in time

952
00:40:39,320 --> 00:40:41,520
and died a heroic death for his country.

953
00:40:45,600 --> 00:40:46,880
Sun Huaiyi...

954
00:40:47,720 --> 00:40:49,520
Sun Huaiyi died for the country?

955
00:40:51,760 --> 00:40:52,800
Originally,

956
00:40:53,000 --> 00:40:54,920
the Military Commission met yesterday

957
00:40:54,920 --> 00:40:55,960
to discuss

958
00:40:56,160 --> 00:40:59,080
posthumously awarding Sun Huaiyi the rank of General.

959
00:40:59,080 --> 00:41:01,720
Now, because of your report,

960
00:41:02,440 --> 00:41:05,760
the posthumous award process is indefinitely suspended.

961
00:41:06,360 --> 00:41:09,360
If we stir things up today...

962
00:41:09,920 --> 00:41:11,250
Announcing to the world

963
00:41:11,320 --> 00:41:12,800
that General Sun is to blame

964
00:41:12,800 --> 00:41:14,720
for the failure of the Battle of Shanghai,

965
00:41:14,720 --> 00:41:17,880
and demoting him after his death

966
00:41:18,320 --> 00:41:20,650
will probably make all the generals think

967
00:41:20,840 --> 00:41:23,400
he is out of sight, out of mind, and we settle accounts later.

968
00:41:23,400 --> 00:41:26,260
This will inevitably hurt the soldiers' feelings.

969
00:41:27,720 --> 00:41:28,680
Report!

970
00:41:29,120 --> 00:41:30,050
Mrs. Sun is here.

971
00:41:36,280 --> 00:41:37,120
Mrs. Sun.

972
00:41:43,920 --> 00:41:45,250
Deputy Minister Huang.

973
00:41:46,640 --> 00:41:47,640
Huaiyi.

974
00:41:48,120 --> 00:41:49,580
Mrs. Sun, my condolences.

975
00:41:49,760 --> 00:41:50,880
Huaiyi's coffin

976
00:41:51,360 --> 00:41:53,160
will arrive in Hankou tomorrow.

977
00:41:53,320 --> 00:41:54,200
I know.

978
00:41:55,080 --> 00:41:56,280
I will go to Hankou.

979
00:41:57,080 --> 00:41:59,040
Minister He will also go to Hankou.

980
00:41:59,520 --> 00:42:02,240
The Military Commission is actively preparing

981
00:42:02,640 --> 00:42:04,000
for Huaiyi's funeral.

982
00:42:05,440 --> 00:42:07,700
I've been married to Huaiyi for 15 years,

983
00:42:08,280 --> 00:42:10,200
but we were rarely together.

984
00:42:10,400 --> 00:42:11,960
Since the war broke out,

985
00:42:12,240 --> 00:42:14,200
he hasn't been home once.

986
00:42:15,400 --> 00:42:17,160
I raised two children alone.

987
00:42:18,160 --> 00:42:20,280
I waited for him day and night.

988
00:42:20,760 --> 00:42:22,760
I never expected that what came back

989
00:42:23,040 --> 00:42:24,680
would be a coffin.

990
00:42:25,320 --> 00:42:26,040
Mom.

991
00:42:26,840 --> 00:42:28,320
Mom, stop crying.

992
00:42:29,120 --> 00:42:30,520
Dad is a great hero.

993
00:42:30,880 --> 00:42:32,520
We should be proud of him.

994
00:42:33,520 --> 00:42:34,650
I've made up my mind.

995
00:42:34,760 --> 00:42:36,080
I'm going to join the army

996
00:42:36,080 --> 00:42:37,680
and fight the Japanese like Dad.

997
00:42:37,680 --> 00:42:38,640
Nonsense.

998
00:42:39,040 --> 00:42:40,280
If you join the army,

999
00:42:40,880 --> 00:42:42,160
for the rest of my life,

1000
00:42:42,760 --> 00:42:44,000
who can I rely on?

1001
00:42:48,320 --> 00:42:49,780
Mrs. Sun, my condolences.

1002
00:42:49,800 --> 00:42:51,600
Please take care of your health.

1003
00:42:53,040 --> 00:42:53,920
Don't worry.

1004
00:42:54,440 --> 00:42:55,700
For Huaiyi's funeral,

1005
00:42:56,320 --> 00:42:59,080
I will do my best to arrange it.
